      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ZINFANDEL DASH (1) was checked in the run and safely held when fourth (31.63) in a Grade 6 over 531m at this track. Can find winning form here. GOLDIE RUSTY (2) finished third last time (23.10) at this track after winning at her previous two outings. Has a good record at this journey. The form out of her last race has been franked. Leading player again. URANA JAM DONUT (8) was safely held in tougher company last start at this track, but prior to that won by 1.75 lengths at Angle Park (19.94) beating Binnaway Wizard in a Grade 6 on April 6. Has good speed and will be prominent from out wide. Better than last start and can bounce back. SEBON DISCO (4) should be thereabouts after filling a top-three at this track and distance most recently.",
